casebody.head_matter:
COAST CANDIDATES PAC, et al., petitioners,
v.
OHIO ELECTIONS COMMISSION, et al.
No. 13-1066.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 23, 2014.
Case below, 543 Fed.Appx. 490.
On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit for further consideration in light of Susan B. Anthony List v. Driehaus, 573 U.S. ----, 134 S.Ct. 2334, --- L.E.2d ---- (2014).
